    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer566150606" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2649480319232295816">This was the most inspiring book i have ever read. Pedro wasn&apos;t someone who was sick and felt bad for himself. He realized he was sick, and wanted to make a difference. I truly think we can all learn from him. When something goes wrong in our life we need to learn not to morn constantly. Instead think of the positives that can come out of it.Pedro did not only have aids, he educated about his aids. Letting people know the facts and the lies. Yes Aids is an illness, and usually does lead to death</span>
  <span id="freeText2649480319232295816" style="display:none">This was the most inspiring book i have ever read. Pedro wasn't someone who was sick and felt bad for himself. He realized he was sick, and wanted to make a difference. I truly think we can all learn from him. When something goes wrong in our life we need to learn not to morn constantly. Instead think of the positives that can come out of it.Pedro did not only have aids, he educated about his aids. Letting people know the facts and the lies. Yes Aids is an illness, and usually does lead to death. But, Pedro overcame that.</span>
